{"id": "1353352361111720027", "channel_id": "1353352361111720027", "type": 0, "author_id": "870225701855436801", "author_name": "ahuahuahua", "author_bot": false, "content": "日安我是菜狗\n近日徵集攻略以及新主線篇章逼使得狗開始了他的星辰坐牢之旅\n為了應付對面逆天數值於是把四小強全部拉到了80級\n瘋狂預兆的部分是7/6/0/0\n靈塑的部分則是都沒有點\n其它部份請見附圖\n\n以下攻略：\n汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪\n（翻譯：建議不要玩這一隊，不然等到只會汪汪叫的時候就已經來不及了。）\n\n另外就是不要踏進星辰篇我真不知道那東西是怎麼樣可以設計出來的", "timestamp": "2025-03-23T12:59:06.960000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 19}, {"emoji": "😡", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}, {"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [{"id": "1353352361547923507", "filename": "Screenshot_20250318_002349.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 882553, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1353352361111720027/1353352361547923507/Screenshot_20250318_002349.jpg?ex=69cbc51b&is=69ca739b&hm=5847be7ca27a396ac3cc786efab270c6526acee039791167d13728b8f1f75471&"}, {"id": "1353352362286252122", "filename": "Screenshot_20250318_010551.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 849437, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1353352361111720027/1353352362286252122/Screenshot_20250318_010551.jpg?ex=69cbc51b&is=69ca739b&hm=c40999701ff66a5d40632151a57af554f74617f2a3d45d704161048d339352ec&"}, {"id": "1353352362839773280", "filename": "Screenshot_20250318_110744.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 896236, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1353352361111720027/1353352362839773280/Screenshot_20250318_110744.jpg?ex=69cbc51b&is=69ca739b&hm=80254e0fd326c3ad09308663b99d526486375b11c729ca27175918db13986a13&"}, {"id": "1353352363452272761", "filename": "Screenshot_20250320_031716.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 881196, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1353352361111720027/1353352363452272761/Screenshot_20250320_031716.jpg?ex=69cbc51b&is=69ca739b&hm=93fd358e926c2fc75677c917e7b717c7